relation: Darrow3 - #78 Stepping outside, Ness encounters Picky, who has become a victim of a broken family after the recent events. With his father and brother having ditched home for their own selfish desires, all that's left is him and Lardna. A home that, surely, is more than frightening than zombie Threed any day of the week.
Darrow3 - #79 Returning to Threed once more, Jeff finally reunites with the Sky Runner...which has been the victim of an unexpected accident.

Darrow3 - #80 With the next goal in mind, the party leaves Eagleland bound for Winters so they can modify the Sky Runner for the next leg of the journey. Perhaps they may even find more than they expected during this little side trip.
Darrow3 - #81 Having arrived at Winters, Jeff reunites with his father at long last. Of course, knowing Dr. Andonuts' track record of following his son's life, the result is...less than joyous.
Darrow3 - #82 Although Dr. Andonuts is not much of a family man, he still does care for those around him. Especially neanderthals that just happen to share their jerky with him.
